Verified:
1. Stage isolation: changing PLACE_DENSITY doesn't rebuild synth
2. config.mk changes detected automatically (no manual invalidation)
3. Parser changes NOT detected (known issue, needs repo rule fix)
4. All 28 bazel-orfs tests pass
5. RTLIL stats: gcd=24K lines to swerv_wrapper=1.5M lines

